本の女性声優。東京都出身。賢プロダクション所属。\r\n\r\n首都大学東京（現・東京都立大学）法学部卒業。\r\n\r\nスクールデュオ卒業。2015年4月1日より賢プロダクション所属。\r\n\r\n教員免許状（中学・高等学校一種）を取得している。\r\n\r\n特技はDTPデザイン（Illustrator、Photoshop）で、広報・デザイン関連で就労した経験がある。趣味は三味線、端唄、クラフトビール。他にKinKi Kids、黒猫、小旅行が好き。高尾山の近くで自然に囲まれて育ったため、花の名前にも詳しい。","career":["seiyu"],"id":60393,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":199568},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/58/03/202918_crt_8I28k.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/58/03/202918_crt_8I28k.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/58/03/202918_crt_8I28k.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/58/03/202918_crt_8I28k.jpg"},"name":"目張きいと","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/06/1f/61535_prsn_fcN0E.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/06/1f/61535_prsn_fcN0E.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/06/1f/61535_prsn_fcN0E.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/06/1f/61535_prsn_fcN0E.jpg"},"name":"和久野愛佳","short_summary":"出身地：愛知県\r\n趣味：歌、物件の間取りを見る、ゲーム\r\n特技：イラスト","career":["seiyu"],"id":61535,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":202918},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/1d/2f/202919_crt_3pKMZ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1d/2f/202919_crt_3pKMZ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1d/2f/202919_crt_3pKMZ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/1d/2f/202919_crt_3pKMZ.jpg"},"name":"笠呉たお","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/dc/cc/80924_prsn_PwCe0.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/dc/cc/80924_prsn_PwCe0.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/dc/cc/80924_prsn_PwCe0.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/dc/cc/80924_prsn_PwCe0.jpg"},"name":"原涼歌","short_summary":"アプトプロ所属。","career":["seiyu"],"id":80924,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":202919},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg"},"name":"角谷喜","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894"},"name":"飛田展男","short_summary":"飛田 展男（とびた のぶお、1959年11月6日 - ）は、日本の声優、ナレーターであり、舞台俳優。アーツビジョン所属。\r\n茨城県水戸市出身。水戸市立三の丸小学校、茨城中学校・高等学校卒業。駒澤大学文学部歴史学科中退。体重55kg。血液型はAB型。愛称は「飛ちゃん」。\r\n\r\n飞田展男，可以说是日本男声优中的“变色龙”。他的角色反差极大，最为夸张的对比就是《安琪莉可》中的水之守护圣卢米埃和《烈火之炎》中的土门，一个美一个丑，一个柔弱一个健壮，一个温柔一个暴躁，一个优雅一个粗鲁，简直就是两个极端，令人怎么也无法相信这是同一位声优的演绎，但事实就是如此。飞田展男利用发音位置的变化控制声音效果，再辅以气声和力度，塑造出截然相反类型的人物。从控制发音变化的技巧来说，飞田展男是独一无二的。","career":["seiyu"],"id":4167,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":202920},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/52/29/203532_crt_dg9iw.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/52/29/203532_crt_dg9iw.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/52/29/203532_crt_dg9iw.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/52/29/203532_crt_dg9iw.jpg"},"name":"初鮎羽果","summary":"","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/76/24/32639_prsn_U39V2.jpg?r=1710509264"},"name":"遠野ひかる","short_summary":"日本の女性声優。響所属。東京都出身。\r\n\r\n小学生時代に音読の宿題を父親に褒められたことをきっかけに、漠然と声の仕事を意識するようになり、高校生時代に多数のアニメ作品に触れて声優になることを決意する。その後、およそ7年に渡り、様々なオーディションを受けては落選を繰り返すが、最初の決意は揺るがず、遂に2017年に響の新人声優発掘プロジェクトのオーディションに合格し、響所属となった。同期には紡木吏佐がいる。\r\n\r\n初めて声を当てた作品は、アプリゲーム『トリプルモンスターズ』のメリュジーナ･マーリン役である。\r\n\r\n2018年11月、紡木と共にブシロード風邪予防大使に任命された。\r\n\r\n2022年12月、野本ほたると共にTikTokで動画投稿を始めた。","career":["seiyu"],"id":32639,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":203532}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/80/9f/199567_crt_ld7hL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/80/9f/199567_crt_ld7hL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/80/9f/199567_crt_ld7hL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/80/9f/199567_crt_ld7hL.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"常連客(老婆)","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"常客(老婆婆)"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":199567,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/82/a5/202920_crt_vItjQ.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"角谷喜","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"角谷喜"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":202920,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/bf/14/198248_crt_33BBp.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bf/14/198248_crt_33BBp.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bf/14/198248_crt_33BBp.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/bf/14/198248_crt_33BBp.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"那色の母親","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"那色的妈妈"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":198248,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_y